  <RimMind.Storyteller.UI.EnableIntervalTrigger.Desc>Request AI to select events at random intervals based on MTB (Mean Time Between). When disabled, the storyteller won't auto-trigger AI requests, but manual trigger still works.</RimMind.Storyteller.UI.EnableIntervalTrigger.Desc>
