  <RimMind.Storyteller.UI.EnableEventNotification.Desc>When the storyteller selects a threat event, send a notification to the request overlay. Players can choose an emotional reaction, which affects narrative tension and future event selection.</RimMind.Storyteller.UI.EnableEventNotification.Desc>
